Notebook[{
Cell[TextData[{
 "I will use double-struck M (\[DoubleStruckCapitalM], \[AliasIndicator]dsM\
\[AliasIndicator]) to mean a bunch of equations or ODEs.\nUnits :  \[HBar] = \
1 \n\[Omega] is the energy splitting between two states. For the purpose of \
solving ODE numerically (ParametricNDSolveValue) it is convenient to set it \
to 1.\nTaking \[CapitalOmega]\[Element]Real for now. I am using conventions \
in PvdS where E(t) = ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["E", "0"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "3f2a1989-9f58-5046-9c92-3b48cbda55ec"],
 "cos(\[Omega]t), so \[CapitalOmega] is the Rabi frequency for population.\n\
Frequency of the drive \[Nu] = \[Omega] + \[Delta] (where \[Delta] is \
dimensionless - the actual detuning is \[Delta]*\[Omega])."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.972869765147604*^9, 3.9728698220036774`*^9}, {
  3.972869853894743*^9, 3.972869900931942*^9}, {3.9728699370198536`*^9, 
  3.9728699387369823`*^9}, {3.9728705942896595`*^9, 3.9728706295260696`*^9}, {
  3.9728724162564106`*^9, 3.9728724348646297`*^9}, {3.972988443263815*^9, 
  3.972988504379553*^9}, {3.9729885473740253`*^9, 3.972988612272869*^9}, {
  3.978206916987955*^9, 3.97820695952886*^9}, {3.9782077272886696`*^9, 
  3.9782077379382553`*^9}, {3.9782078359438457`*^9, 3.978207862136408*^9}, {
  3.9782079079831543`*^9, 3.9782079289240227`*^9}, {3.978491347087511*^9, 
  3.978491350008465*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c7d3186c-9769-bd47-80b5-\
fd6a35c2afdf"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Two level system", "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.972999840537899*^9, 
  3.972999842971155*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c89c9348-f4b1-8c43-99d1-\
5132a43ef0fe"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "All the calculations below eventually look at the population in one of the \
state. As we have talked about in the 2025/12/02 meeting, there are some \
complications if we look at the inner product of the TLS state with some \
other basis state (in our case, the TLS states are Bloch states ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  TemplateBox[{
    SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", "nk"]},
   "Ket"]],ExpressionUUID->"757cb4fd-37d1-d44f-a3c7-261dbf383009"],
 ", and the \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]some other basis state\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] is the plane wave component ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["e", "ikx"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "dc334388-411c-1244-965d-6a7818cad0dd"],
 " where k is within the first BZ). See photo from the meeting page."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.973766352314005*^9, 3.9737663617117786`*^9}, {
  3.9737663958995457`*^9, 3.9737665608206577`*^9}, {3.9737665964937515`*^9, 
  3.9737666245273113`*^9}, {3.9737669295351906`*^9, 
  3.973766934433529*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8d8aa1a2-991a-9a4b-ac28-\
2242faab4fa7"],

Cell["\<\
No coherence (our case): we accidentally cancelled out the cross-terms \
resulting from coherences by doing the opposite shaking, since starting the \
shake in the opposite direction is the same as adding a \[Pi] phase shift to \
the modulation, i.e. \[CapitalOmega]\[RightArrow]-\[CapitalOmega], resulting \
in cross-terms with opposite signs. In this case, the inner product \
differences looks the same as the population plots, but with reduced contrast.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9737666558874683`*^9, 
  3.9737669038764744`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a9ae54ab-c14f-3b4e-a114-\
72f3a6faebb3"],

Cell["\<\
With coherence: no simple relations - we need to also know the inner products \
explicitly.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9737666558874683`*^9, 
  3.973766926766182*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3edbddc3-8104-7940-8919-\
e2f51ad82b94"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Solving the ODE", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9728708693822174`*^9, 
  3.972870873488434*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d0883f88-06b5-7f4c-974a-\
105536aaed2e"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Defining the equations", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9728709131522064`*^9, 3.972870929735197*^9}, 
   3.972870974277895*^9},ExpressionUUID->"9089a735-5d84-aa44-86a1-\
bb0eaf7e0488"],

Cell["\<\
The original ODE to be solved (in the frame rotating at the frequency of the \
drive), see e.g. Childress.
Initial conditions listed separately.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9728702578836727`*^9, 3.9728703002790585`*^9}, {
  3.9728704937701607`*^9, 3.9728705025774593`*^9}, {3.97820684204652*^9, 
  3.978206845841894*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fabd680c-196e-b74f-8eef-\
7c1234cbf83f"],

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]TLSnoRWA", "=", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"I", "*", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"c2", "'"}], "[", "t", "]"}]}], "==", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"-", "\[Delta]"}], "*", 
        RowBox[{"c2", "[", "t", "]"}]}], "-", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"(", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"\[CapitalOmega]", "/", "2"}], "+", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"\[CapitalOmega]", "/", "2"}], "*", 
           RowBox[{"Exp", "[", 
            RowBox[{"2", "*", "I", "*", "\[Nu]", "*", "t"}], "]"}]}]}], ")"}],
         "*", 
        RowBox[{"c1", "[", "t", "]"}]}]}]}], ",", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"I", "*", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"c1", "'"}], "[", "t", "]"}]}], "==", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"-", 
        RowBox[{"(", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"\[CapitalOmega]", "/", "2"}], "+", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"\[CapitalOmega]", "/", "2"}], "*", 
           RowBox[{"Exp", "[", 
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"-", "2"}], "*", "I", "*", "\[Nu]", "*", "t"}], 
            "]"}]}]}], ")"}]}], "*", 
       RowBox[{"c2", "[", "t", "]"}]}]}]}], "}"}]}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]InitCon", "=", 
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"c1", "[", "0", "]"}], "==", "1"}], ",", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"c2", "[", "0", "]"}], "==", "0"}]}], "}"}]}], ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.972869689830824*^9, 3.972869695176832*^9}, {
   3.972869833144903*^9, 3.9728698433910713`*^9}, {3.9728699055925827`*^9, 
   3.9728699720312805`*^9}, 3.972870143408457*^9, {3.9729886224914856`*^9, 
   3.9729886346565495`*^9}, {3.9729944348857327`*^9, 3.97299443546187*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[1]:=",ExpressionUUID->"1f292889-855e-5541-9656-8ff2a553aad8"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "RWA amounts to setting the counter-rotating terms (terms with ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"\[PlusMinus]", "2"}], "\[ImaginaryI]\[Nu]t"}]], 
   TraditionalForm]],
  FormatType->TraditionalForm,ExpressionUUID->
  "c835194f-50a0-1349-87de-c84e82dc0e7a"],
 ") to zero."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9728703091815033`*^9, 3.9728703686971016`*^9}, {
  3.972870436556389*^9, 3.9728704465646267`*^9}, {3.9728707108509026`*^9, 
  3.972870784216732*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"88ff49f1-ae74-fe43-b874-\
6a4d3419e92f"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{"\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]noRWA", "=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"Join", "[", 
    RowBox[{
    "\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]TLSnoRWA", ",", 
     "\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]InitCon"}], "]"}], "/.", 
   RowBox[{"\[Nu]", "->", 
    RowBox[{"1", "+", "\[Delta]"}]}]}]}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]RWA", "=", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Join", "[", 
     RowBox[{
     "\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]TLSnoRWA", ",", 
      "\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]InitCon"}], "]"}], "/.", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"Exp", "[", 
        RowBox[{"2", "*", "I", "*", "\[Nu]", "*", "t"}], "]"}], "->", "0"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"Exp", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"-", "2"}], "*", "I", "*", "\[Nu]", "*", "t"}], "]"}], "->", 
       "0"}]}], "}"}]}]}], ";"}]}], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9727524889710217`*^9, 3.9727525369709034`*^9}, {
   3.97275256896986*^9, 3.9727528122545605`*^9}, {3.972752906839569*^9, 
   3.972752906918947*^9}, {3.9727529409809*^9, 3.9727529410451336`*^9}, {
   3.9727529800703773`*^9, 3.972753124250656*^9}, 3.9727531634536076`*^9, {
   3.97275326334437*^9, 3.9727533098839417`*^9}, 3.9727533864579124`*^9, {
   3.9727534730552387`*^9, 3.9727534829140835`*^9}, {3.9727535180414696`*^9, 
   3.972753559297163*^9}, {3.9727539049868793`*^9, 3.9727539146452274`*^9}, {
   3.9727543785715446`*^9, 3.972754406757082*^9}, 3.972754465463709*^9, {
   3.972754581069847*^9, 3.972754585070257*^9}, {3.972754661011957*^9, 
   3.9727546618427544`*^9}, {3.9728702045880795`*^9, 3.972870242495119*^9}, 
   3.972870534953573*^9, {3.9729891649767075`*^9, 3.972989177317383*^9}, {
   3.978489938796316*^9, 3.97848997672665*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[3]:=",ExpressionUUID->"f89f3b4f-99ca-b34f-93ad-b18d9f77c938"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox["c2", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], "[", "t", "]"}]}], "\[Equal]", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"-", 
      RowBox[{"(", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"(", 
         RowBox[{
          FractionBox["\[CapitalOmega]", "2"], "+", 
          RowBox[{
           FractionBox["1", "2"], " ", 
           SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
            RowBox[{"2", " ", "\[ImaginaryI]", " ", "t", " ", 
             RowBox[{"(", 
              RowBox[{"1", "+", "\[Delta]"}], ")"}]}]], " ", 
           "\[CapitalOmega]"}]}], ")"}], " ", 
        RowBox[{"c1", "[", "t", "]"}]}], ")"}]}], "-", 
     RowBox[{"\[Delta]", " ", 
      RowBox[{"c2", "[", "t", "]"}]}]}]}], ",", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"\[ImaginaryI]", " ", 
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox["c1", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], "[", "t", "]"}]}], "\[Equal]", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"(", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"-", 
        FractionBox["\[CapitalOmega]", "2"]}], "-", 
       RowBox[{
        FractionBox["1", "2"], " ", 
        SuperscriptBox["\[ExponentialE]", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", "2"}], " ", "\[ImaginaryI]", " ", "t", " ", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
           RowBox[{"1", "+", "\[Delta]"}], ")"}]}]], " ", 
        "\[CapitalOmega]"}]}], ")"}], " ", 
     RowBox[{"c2", "[", "t", "]"}]}]}], ",", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"c1", "[", "0", "]"}], "\[Equal]", "1"}], ",", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"c2", "[", "0", "]"}], "\[Equal]", "0"}]}], "}"}]], "Output",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9729891860879936`*^9, 3.9729892080153885`*^9}, 
   3.972994633750025*^9, 3.973701175402502*^9, 3.9737013282222443`*^9, 
   3.978199800338297*^9, 3.9784880305911674`*^9, {3.978489960407236*^9, 
   3.9784899774670467`*^9}, 3.978491526907963*^9, 3.978799627285757*^9},
 CellLabel->"Out[3]=",ExpressionUUID->"89e0cd3f-430a-404f-8fed-5a9f419a458b"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Analytic solution", "Subsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.972870964379217*^9, 
  3.972870971250025*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0b5589ad-af1e-9b42-9ffc-\
344eb1770a4a"],

Cell["\<\
As we have learned in AMO classes, the RWA simplifies the ODE dramatically, \
and the solution is very simple.
We also see that the equation without the RWA is not easily solvable. This is \
what makes the RWA so useful.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9728709821278286`*^9, 3.9728710559055347`*^9}, {
  3.972988724196314*^9, 
  3.9729887246296806`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6915896a-3ff8-644e-875a-\
6a01f92a979a"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"c1RWAraw", ",", "c2RWAraw"}], "}"}], "=", 
   RowBox[{"DSolveValue", "[", 
    RowBox[{"\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]RWA", ",", 
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{"c1", ",", "c2"}], "}"}], ",", "t"}], "]"}]}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"DSolveValue", "[", 
   RowBox[{"\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]noRWA", ",", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{"c1", ",", "c2"}], "}"}], ",", "t"}], "]"}], 
  RowBox[{"(*", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Doesn", "'"}], "t", " ", "give", " ", "a", " ", "solution"}], 
   "*)"}]}]}], "Input",
 Editable->False,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.972752831795248*^9, 3.9727528501610336`*^9}, {
   3.9727528901202564`*^9, 3.9727529495774918`*^9}, 3.972753100550009*^9, {
